Xper Persuasion                                                               
----------------                                                              
                                                                              
Dox Typed by -BLB-                                                            
                                                                              
                                                                              
3185 AD, in an unknown galaxy flies a little spaceship far from civilisation. 
Xper was the 9th son of the Brave King of the galaxy, who was kidnapped by    
the Evil Burks.                                                               
                                                                              
                                                                              
You are Xper, your task is to escape from Burks Plaza, a shopping mall in     
Virtual Reality Deepspace. You have to fight yourself through 11 arcade action
packed levels of mindblasting terror.                                         
                                                                              
                                                                              
STARTUP                                                                       
                                                                              
                                                                              
Turn on your computer and insert disk 1 of Xper Persuasion in the internal    
diskdrive and wait. Remove all external devices and expansions to free up     
as much memory as posible. After the music has played your will see the       
options page.                                                                 
                                                                              
                                                                              
OPTIONS PAGE                                                                  
                                                                              
                                                                              
Lives 3/5/7 <- The amount of lives to start with.                             
                                                                              
Game Difficulty  Easy/Normal/Hard <- enables you to play the game on your     
                                     personal level.                          
                                                                              
Sounds/Music  On/Off <- play with music and/or sound effects.                 
                                                                              
Start Game <- this doesn't need an explanation i think?                       
                                                                              
                                                                              
                                                                              
