<SPACEBAR> will enables you to select weapons.                                
<RETURN>   will blow the blitzbomb.                                           
<P>        Pause                                                              
<ESC>      Quit game                                                          
                                                                              
                                                                              
During gameplay collect the numerous icons for special weapons.               
Pressing <SPACEBAR> will enable the current highlighted weapon,               
pressing <RETURN> will blow the blizbomb, but be carefull you only got        
5 of them at the start.                                                       
                                                                              
                                                                              
